data.description: Come check out this outstanding investment opportunity. This property is currently zoned as a 1 family, but it will be up to buyer to get it zoned for a 2 family with the proper permits. This house does have two spacious, move in ready apartments! Both apartments have recently been updated with fresh paint, freshly refinished hardwoods, and much more. The attached apartment would be perfect for an in law situation, or rent it out and let your tenant pay your mortgage! The main house boasts 4 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, living room, eat in kitchen, mud room, and a large deck.  There are two bedrooms downstairs and two bedrooms upstairs with full bathrooms on each floor. The attached apartment has 2 bedrooms, family room, a kitchen/laundry room and a private deck. This property also has  a spacious 2 car garage, a large fully fenced yard, and separate driveways, separate utilities, and private entrances! Each unit has it's own laundry hookups and newer furnace. Conveniently located in Park Hill neighborhood which is on bus routes. Don't miss out on this amazing investment opportunity!
